ormal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人話關你事呀，係要你了解下皮膚係咩一回事<br />\n係要你知唔係乾到出油所以保濕過一陣就無用呀<br />\n要係要補濕，但係唔係補完濕就唔會出油<br />\n你保濕果下角質充滿水份一定好靚好飽滿唔會出油，但你角質根本鎖唔到水，結果啲水份流失完咪打回原形<br />\n<br />\n要解決問題要了解自己皮膚，了解用嘅產品成份，同埋之間產生嘅反應<br />\n無心機了解嘅你就由佢繼續「總之」油到煎蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3227b65bd3bacbb206e26112ffa99c1b68c6e653","tid":270552,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>潔臉做足 補濕做足 鎖水做足 去角質做足 你仲想我點呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪錯晒，油肌唔控油做保濕做乜鬼</blockquote><br />\n油乾性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n油乾性你講出黎唔覺得怪嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗你想講嘅係一般人講嘅「乾到出油」？<br />\nSorry,係我嘅世界無呢種膚質<br />\n乾到出油根本係油肌黎，因為人為因素搞到水油唔平衡，而唔係因為乾所以出油咁直接<br />\n如果唔係呢個世界點會有乾肌，乾肌就個個都出油啦照咁講，係咪先</blockquote><br />\n乾肌岀唔到油關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之我就係唔補濕就岀油</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人話關你事呀，係要你了解下皮膚係咩一回事<br />\n係要你知唔係乾到出油所以保濕過一陣就無用呀<br />\n要係要補濕，但係唔係補完濕就唔會出油<br />\n你保濕果下角質充滿水份一定好靚好飽滿唔會出油，但你角質根本鎖唔到水，結果啲水份流失完咪打回原形<br />\n<br />\n要解決問題要了解自己皮膚，了解用嘅產品成份，同埋之間產生嘅反應<br />\n無心機了解嘅你就由佢繼續「總之」油到煎蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌了解了解 點了解先得㗎？講成大段野都無main point <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a6c8d4fa8a0b1212d67149262c5abec314628a","tid":270552,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人話關你事呀，係要你了解下皮膚係咩一回事<br />\n係要你知唔係乾到出油所以保濕過一陣就無用呀<br />\n要係要補濕，但係唔係補完濕就唔會出油<br />\n你保濕果下角質充滿水份一定好靚好飽滿唔會出油，但你角質根本鎖唔到水，結果啲水份流失完咪打回原形<br />\n<br />\n要解決問題要了解自己皮膚，了解用嘅產品成份，同埋之間產生嘅反應<br />\n無心機了解嘅你就由佢繼續「總之」油到煎蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌了解了解 點了解先得㗎？講成大段野都無main point <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無main point?<br />\n餵埋俾你啦<br />\nMain point1:無乾到出油<br />\nMain point 2:補濕唔會減少出油，只會令保好濕果下皮膚好靚仔<br />\nMain point 3:你角質鎖唔到水<br />\n點了解，睇書囉睇journal 囉，唔岩嘅而家科技咁發達上網睇囉"},{"pid":"ae89ac6a056f4b80e15944d5fa83d2fc79ae89e1","tid":270552,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"原來係假膠黎，係我認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a85e9a3d503d8f1767b5b008388cd571676092","tid":270552,"uid":1435